Dialogue.text: Good morning, Sector 7! Today is the 5th day of Gnarl, and my birthday! The big 4-0-0.

Dialogue489.text: What I want for my birthday is to see Overlord Aso in person for the first time ever. Too bad that's not scheduled for my podtown for another 87 years!

Dialogue498.text: In other news, scientists say that the CX-6 Virus can be spread through asymptomatic individuals.

Dialogue507.text: No cough, but still infectious? Could be!

Dialogue517.text: Apparently most are contagious days before showing any symptoms, and some never show symptoms.
